nce whose first term " }{TEXT 303 1 "a" }{TEXT -1 89 " is the last thr
ee digits of your social security number (S) and and whose common rati
on " }{TEXT 304 1 "r" }{TEXT -1 120 " is the ratio of your number the \+
month of your birthdate to the number of the day-of-the-month of your \+
birthdate (M/D). " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 ">
