" 0 "" {TEXT -1 19 "3.  (8 points) The " }{TEXT 256 9 "Fibonacci" }
{TEXT -1 333 " sequence is neither arithmetic for geometric.  It is a \+
recursive sequence, whose first two terms are both 1 and for which the
reafter each successive term is the sum of the two preceding terms.  T
hus, the sequence takes on the form \{1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, . . . \}.  Use
 Maple to construct the first thirty terms of the Fibonacci sequence.
" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 21 "f[1] := 1; f[2] := 1;" }
