$-%'vectorG6#7(\"\"\"\"\"!!\"\"!\"#!\"$!\"%-F'6#7(F+F*\"\"#\"\"$\"\"%
\"\"&" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }{TEXT 271 43 "\nHence,
 rowspace of A and column space of  " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "A^T" "6#)%\"AG%
\"TG" }{TEXT 272 16 " are the same.\n " }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" 
