F8F*F8F+F*,$*(F-F,F8F*F8F+F*,$*(F0F,F8F*F8F+F*,$*(\"\"%F,F8F*F8F+F*%)v
alue~isGF1" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6'-%'vectorG6#7(,$*&\"#:!
